20
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:31,520
Pingjing Duke, please get up.

21
00:02:31,890 --> 00:02:34,190
It is my duty to discover and appoint talents.

22
00:02:34,190 --> 00:02:35,510
You're too modest.

23
00:02:35,630 --> 00:02:36,940
But I don't know

24
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,640
