32
00:03:06,670 --> 00:03:08,150
But now it's the only way

33
00:03:08,150 --> 00:03:09,400
to keep you safe.

34
00:03:09,900 --> 00:03:11,940
Besides, in order to protect you,

35
00:03:12,710 --> 00:03:14,840
