36
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:17,650
So now you can only go forward, not back down.

37
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:18,380
Understand?

38
00:03:18,380 --> 00:03:20,500
Yes, I understand.

39
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:25,430
I'll make a three-day military pledge for you.

40
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:26,990
Can you make it?

41
00:03:27,630 --> 00:03:28,430
Three days?

42
00:03:28,770 --> 00:03:30,360
You have followed Lord Ge for several years

43
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,010
in Yuanzhou.

44
00:03:32,430 --> 00:03:36,160
I believe you can prove yourself.

45
00:03:44,020 --> 00:03:46,020
I thought if I joined the North Clan,

46
00:03:46,470 --> 00:03:49,400
we would have fulfilled our ambitions and survived.

47
00:03:50,270 --> 00:03:53,110
I didn't expect it to be a dead game.

48
00:03:54,250 --> 00:03:55,329
This Ka Dun

49
00:03:56,210 --> 00:03:59,940
wants me to fight against Si Yilin,

50
00:04:00,150 --> 00:04:01,880
then he can take advantage of it

51
