78
00:06:20,510 --> 00:06:22,570
I don't know what his current name is.

79
00:06:22,710 --> 00:06:25,190
But his former name was Lei Hong.

80
00:06:25,690 --> 00:06:27,820
I can recognize him even if he turns into ashes.

81
00:06:27,820 --> 00:06:30,420
He used to be the Deputy Commander of Yuanzhou.

82
00:06:32,150 --> 00:06:32,820
Hurry!

83
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:36,980
At this rate,

84
00:06:37,020 --> 00:06:38,480
our city will be in danger.

85
00:06:38,940 --> 00:06:40,400
We can't let them get any closer.

86
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:42,560
My Lord, please give the order to shoot the arrows.

87
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:43,690
If we order to shoot,

88
00:06:43,950 --> 00:06:46,080
the captives at the front will be dead.

89
00:06:46,150 --> 00:06:47,150
What should we do?

90
00:06:47,630 --> 00:06:49,159
We can't hurt the captives.

91
00:06:51,230 --> 00:06:53,590
Everyone, without my order,

92
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:55,610
you mustn't shoot.

93
00:06:55,909 --> 00:06:56,510
Yes.

94
00:06:57,710 --> 00:06:58,640
Second Brother.

95
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:01,890
Look at those captives.

96
00:07:02,140 --> 00:07:04,580
Which unit were they originally from?

97
00:07:05,450 --> 00:07:08,110
They were from Ming Hui's and Fang Jin's armies.

98
00:07:08,940 --> 00:07:11,510
There are injured soldiers and some commoners.

99
00:07:11,510 --> 00:07:12,570
If that's the case,

100
00:07:13,090 --> 00:07:15,200
they were all soldiers of Zichuan.

101
00:07:15,790 --> 00:07:16,590
That's right.

102
00:07:22,310 --> 00:07:23,550
Guys, come with me.

103
00:07:23,850 --> 00:07:25,050
Baichuan, stay here.

104
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,460
Your Highness.

105
00:07:35,990 --> 00:07:38,830
Pingjing Duke only brought a group of rebels to attack this time.

106
00:07:38,830 --> 00:07:39,560
Will it work?

107
00:07:40,150 --> 00:07:41,409
If he wins,

108
00:07:41,870 --> 00:07:44,330
we can seize the chance to chase the enemies.

109
00:07:44,590 --> 00:07:45,300
If he loses,

110
00:07:46,530 --> 00:07:47,590
we can also consume

111
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:49,200
some of Si Yilin's troops.

112
00:07:49,659 --> 00:07:52,270
We can also find out what's going on in Payi.

113
00:07:53,110 --> 00:07:53,640
Besides,

114
00:07:54,870 --> 00:07:56,870
it's not our soldiers who will die.

115
00:07:57,630 --> 00:07:59,690
They're just dogs biting each other.

116
00:08:00,630 --> 00:08:04,040
I admire your move, Your Highness.

117
00:08:05,220 --> 00:08:08,670
But Pingjing Duke

118
00:08:09,540 --> 00:08:10,540
is so mean.

119
00:08:11,380 --> 00:08:15,840
How could he come up with such a dirty trick to use the captives to attack the city?

120
00:08:16,510 --> 00:08:18,340
Lei Hong is less than ten miles away

121
00:08:18,340 --> 00:08:19,330
from Payi.

122
00:08:19,590 --> 00:08:21,900
If Si Yilin couldn't bear to kill the captives,

123
00:08:21,900 --> 00:08:23,460
the rebels in Yuanzhou

124
00:08:23,510 --> 00:08:25,470
could easily approach Payi.

125
00:08:26,330 --> 00:08:27,250
Si Yilin

126
00:08:28,280 --> 00:08:31,040
is always hiding like a coward.

127
00:08:31,880 --> 00:08:35,140
If Pingjing Duke can make him take the initiative to attack

128
00:08:35,630 --> 00:08:37,090
and open the gate himself,

129
00:08:38,190 --> 00:08:38,909
by then,

130
00:08:39,740 --> 00:08:42,940
we can easily take down Payi.

131
00:08:46,660 --> 00:08:48,430
Hurry up.

132
00:08:54,310 --> 00:08:55,670
Who allowed you to shoot arrows?

133
00:08:55,670 --> 00:08:57,710
My Lord, we can't wait any longer.

134
00:08:58,040 --> 00:08:59,840
Xiu is dealing with it, you know?

135
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:01,910
We don't even know where Lord Xiu is now.

136
00:09:01,910 --> 00:09:03,430
According to his usual style,

137
00:09:03,430 --> 00:09:04,820
would he run away

138
00:09:05,070 --> 00:09:06,350
at this critical moment?

139
00:09:06,350 --> 00:09:07,790
I trust my brother.

140
00:09:10,470 --> 00:09:12,350
Don't shoot without my order.

141
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:13,470
Yes.

142
00:09:14,070 --> 00:09:16,000
I have a way to save those captives.

143
00:09:16,420 --> 00:09:19,280
It's a good chance to break the spirit of Lei Hong.

144
00:09:20,070 --> 00:09:21,710
But we need the cooperation

145
00:09:21,710 --> 00:09:23,310
of all the residents in Payi.

146
00:09:23,830 --> 00:09:26,630
Follow my and the Xiu Battalion's arrangement

147
00:09:26,830 --> 00:09:27,690
and cooperate.

148
00:09:27,950 --> 00:09:29,150
From now on,

149
00:09:29,550 --> 00:09:32,110
all of you will obey Lord Xiu

150
00:09:32,290 --> 00:09:33,770
and the Xiu Battalion.

151
00:09:35,130 --> 00:09:37,990
If there is any disobedience, it will be dealt with according to military law.

152
00:09:37,990 --> 00:09:38,630
This way.

153
00:09:39,270 --> 00:09:41,400
Lime powder and chili powder. Come on.

154
00:09:46,830 --> 00:09:47,430
Your turn.

155
00:09:49,350 --> 00:09:50,190
Come on.

156
00:09:57,270 --> 00:09:58,030
Hurry.

157
00:10:01,790 --> 00:10:02,320
This way.

158
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:06,280
Hurry up.

159
00:10:07,220 --> 00:10:08,020
It's choking.

160
00:10:08,670 --> 00:10:09,930
Come on. One more here.

161
00:10:10,910 --> 00:10:12,000
Hurry.

162
00:10:13,310 --> 00:10:13,790
Hurry!

163
00:10:15,710 --> 00:10:17,020
Hurry up.

164
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:20,070
Hurry up.

165
00:10:21,670 --> 00:10:22,790
You're right.

166
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:26,290
Si Yilin still couldn't bear to kill the captives.

167
00:10:26,290 --> 00:10:27,080
At this rate,

168
00:10:27,510 --> 00:10:29,310
we can get close to the city gate soon.

169
00:10:29,310 --> 00:10:30,910
All people have weaknesses.

170
00:10:32,060 --> 00:10:34,580
Although Si Yilin is a general,

171
00:10:34,870 --> 00:10:37,880
he is too soft-hearted and not decisive enough.

172
00:10:38,810 --> 00:10:41,010
He's not as cruel as Di Lin.

173
00:10:48,870 --> 00:10:51,950
Pass my order. Keep moving.

174
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:52,560
Yes!

175
00:10:56,790 --> 00:10:57,910
Full speed ahead!

176
00:11:06,510 --> 00:11:06,990
Hurry!

177
00:11:11,630 --> 00:11:12,160
Hurry up.

178
00:11:14,630 --> 00:11:16,700
Hurry up. Go ahead.

179
00:11:16,730 --> 00:11:17,660
Walk on your own.

180
00:11:21,100 --> 00:11:21,740
Hurry up.

181
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:03,050
What's going on?

182
00:12:04,030 --> 00:12:05,390
Send the messenger to the front to investigate.

183
00:12:05,390 --> 00:12:05,710
Yes.

184
00:12:09,100 --> 00:12:11,820
Firstly, when Lei Hong's vanguard troops

185
00:12:11,880 --> 00:12:13,920
approach within less than two miles of the city,

186
00:12:13,920 --> 00:12:16,340
we will use catapults to launch a large number of smoke bombs

187
00:12:16,340 --> 00:12:18,520
into the area between the vanguard troops

188
00:12:18,520 --> 00:12:19,980
and Lei Hong's main force,

189
00:12:20,270 --> 00:12:21,630
disrupting the enemy's vision

190
00:12:21,630 --> 00:12:23,760
and cutting off their communication.

191
00:12:23,870 --> 00:12:26,330
Since they used to be soldiers of the Zichuan family,

192
00:12:26,330 --> 00:12:28,240
they must be very sensitive to semaphores

193
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:30,070
and horn sounds.

194
00:12:33,780 --> 00:12:34,870
I can read the semaphores.

195
00:12:34,870 --> 00:12:36,110
The gates on both sides are open.

196
00:12:36,110 --> 00:12:37,310
Run to both sides!

197
00:12:40,270 --> 00:12:42,020
Guys, fight them!

198
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:44,960
Don't run!

199
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:48,670
Don't run!

200
00:12:49,150 --> 00:12:50,010
At this moment,

201
00:12:50,100 --> 00:12:52,360
they will quickly meet at the side gates.

202
00:12:52,710 --> 00:12:53,640
Second Brother.

203
00:12:53,700 --> 00:12:55,630
You need to lead the Armored Cavalry

204
00:12:55,630 --> 00:12:56,940
to break out of the main city gate

205
00:12:56,940 --> 00:12:58,830
to attract the attention of the rebels in Yuanzhou

206
00:12:58,830 --> 00:13:01,190
and buy more time for the captives.

207
00:13:14,940 --> 00:13:15,910
Kill!

208
00:13:23,710 --> 00:13:24,310
Come back!

209
00:13:24,350 --> 00:13:25,150
Stop! Stop!

210
00:13:25,670 --> 00:13:26,390
Stop!

211
00:13:27,860 --> 00:13:28,710
Stop!

212
00:13:39,920 --> 00:13:41,880
